seq_instruction:
Explain how one can identify any programming language from a code snippet. 

Consider the following Python code:

if (20 > 18):
  print("20 is greater than 18")

Can you identify the programming language?

Now consider the following code:

if (20 > 18) {
  printf("20 is greater than 18");
}

What programming language is this? Explain why "printf" is used in this context.

